    "Since 2010, RHIC has conducted two rounds of beam energy scan campaigns primarily aimed at investigating the QCD critical point.",
    "The BES programs cover an energy range from √ s NN = 200 GeV to 3.0 GeV, corresponding to a baryonic chemical potential of 20 MeV ≤ B ≤ 750 MeV.",
