    "The experimental results shown as a function of the collision energy are depicted in Fig. 20.",
    "Overall, the ratios of C 4 ∕C 2 for net-protons from collider mode ( √ s NN ≥ 7.7 GeV) [38, 158] and protons from the fixed-target mode decrease as collision energy decreases as dictated by the baryon number conservation."
